<header>Wedded Bliss Budget App</header>
<p>Get started with your own personalized budget app...Tying the Knot Shouldn't Cost You a Fortune</p>
<img src="https://amp.thisisinsider.com/images/5b9eb0ef3cccd11d008b4576-1536-1024.jpg" class="bride-image" width="500" height="300">
<h2>Must Have</h2>

    <ul>
      {{#each weddings}} {{#unless essentials}} {{> weddings/wedding-block essential=true}} {{/unless}} {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2 class="below">Nice to Have</h2>

    <ul>
      {{#each weddings}} {{#if essentials}} {{> weddings/wedding-block essential=false}} {{/if}} {{/each}}
    </ul>

<h2>Add to Your List</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="ca">Item Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="name">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="ca">Amount:</label>
    <input type="text" id="amount" name="amount">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="essential">Must Have versus Nice to Have</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="essentials" value="1" checked> Nice to Have<br>
    <input type="radio" name="essentials" value="0"> Must Have
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Add Item</button>
</form>